# Files accidentally created by pip when a version constraint is parsed as a redirect
# (e.g. `pip install 'pkg>=0.2.36'` from an unquoted shell wrote `=0.2.36`).
=*

# Model artifacts
# Tracked checkpoints live under model_registry/. Keep ad-hoc local zips out of git.
/*.zip
